You are a Principal HRMS Architect, Talent Management Consultant, Government Contract Workforce Specialist, Enterprise Product Architect, Training Consultant, Recruitment Expert, Performance Management Consultant, Database Architect, UI/UX Designer, and Senior Full Stack Engineer.

Design and build a complete Enterprise Talent & Growth Module for a Government Tender Manpower ERP System.

This ERP serves:

- Government Tender Contractors
- Security Agencies
- Facility Management Companies
- Housekeeping Companies
- Contract Labour Providers
- Industrial Workforce Suppliers
- Driver Supply Agencies
- Skilled & Semi-Skilled Labour Contractors

The Talent & Growth module must manage the complete employee journey from recruitment to retirement while supporting 100,000+ employees across multiple government contracts.

